locations.title: Tampa
locations.content:
Thank you for visiting our East Hillsborough webpage.

Our East Hillsborough location is where Taco Bus first hit its brakes, but we’re not stopping until we’ve reached our ultimate destination – your culinary delight.

So stop on by and bring your friends and family along for a trip to authentic Mexican flavor, served fresh and open late!

And if you've got to have it mas rapido, you can save time by ordering online.

Special Events

Taco Bus Brandon has a car show the second Sunday of the month with a DJ playing music from 4pm to 7pm during the summer and 3pm to 6pm during the winter. There are a variety of cars ranging from classics to sports cars and everything in between. So come on out, listen to some music, check out some cars and enjoy a taco while you’re here.
